#Graphs in Google Sheets
Replacing level with panels for google sheets
> #### Practice building graphs in Google Sheets. Create at least one. If you have time and want to explore, try creating a dot plot, bar graph and scatter plot.

## Data Link

#### Use this link to access the school party survey data from previous lessons.
