## Bar Chart
#### Using the pizza party data, create a bar chart by:
#### 1. Highlight the column of data you want to use.
#### 2. Select 'insert' graph from the drop down menu.
#### 3. Select 'bar chart' from the side menu.

<details><summary style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>🔎 Show Me How 🔎</strong></summary> <img src="https://images.code.org/a343e96165703b6c5f3819af77d15a47-image-1731532933733.gif">
</details>

<div style="clear:both;"></div>

---

<img src="https://images.code.org/b5dd1ce9a5e6b3d8122a87a21efc7ab0-image-1731425622735.png" alt="bar chart created in CODAP" width="250px" style="border-radius:10px; float:right; margin: 0 0 40px 40px;">

## Pie Chart

#### Using the pizza party data, create a bar chart by:
#### 1. Highlight the column of data you want to use.
#### 2. Select 'insert' graph from the drop down menu.
#### 3. Select 'pie chart' from the side menu.

<details><summary style="font-size: 18px;"><strong>🔎 Show Me How 🔎</strong></summary> <img src="https://images.code.org/dc6b5337afc103094149798c1a6634f1-image-1731533159844.gif">
</details>

<div style="clear:both;"></div>


